/-- `coeq‚ÇÉ f g h`, for morphisms `f g h : j‚ÇÅ ‚ü∂ j‚ÇÇ`, is an arbitrary choice of object
which admits a morphism `coeq‚ÇÉ_hom f g h : j‚ÇÇ ‚ü∂ coeq‚ÇÉ f g h` such that
